verses.text: Praise waiteth \w for|strong="H1732"\w* thee, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* God, \w in|strong="H1732"\w* Zion; \w And|strong="H1732"\w* \w unto|strong="H1732"\w* thee \w shall|strong="H1732"\w* \w the|strong="H1732"\w* vow \w be|strong="H1732"\w* performed.
\w O|strong="H3068"\w* thou that hearest prayer, \w Unto|strong="H5088"\w* \w thee|strong="H8416"\w* \w shall|strong="H5088"\w* all flesh come.

Iniquities prevail \w against|strong="H8085"\w* \w me|strong="H8085"\w*: \w As|strong="H5704"\w* \w for|strong="H5704"\w* \w our|strong="H3605"\w* transgressions, \w thou|strong="H5704"\w* wilt forgive \w them|strong="H8085"\w*.

Blessed \w is|strong="H1697"\w* \w the|strong="H4480"\w* man whom thou choosest, \w and|strong="H1697"\w* causest \w to|strong="H1697"\w* approach \add unto thee\add*, \w That|strong="H1697"\w* \w he|strong="H4480"\w* \w may|strong="H4480"\w* dwell \w in|strong="H1697"\w* \w thy|strong="H4480"\w* courts: \w We|strong="H1697"\w* \w shall|strong="H1697"\w* \w be|strong="H1697"\w* satisfied \w with|strong="H1697"\w* \w the|strong="H4480"\w* goodness \w of|strong="H1697"\w* \w thy|strong="H4480"\w* house, \w Thy|strong="H4480"\w* holy temple.

\w By|strong="H7126"\w* terrible \w things|strong="H2898"\w* thou wilt answer \w us|strong="H7646"\w* \w in|strong="H1004"\w* righteousness, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* God \w of|strong="H1004"\w* our salvation, Thou \w that|strong="H2691"\w* art \w the|strong="H7126"\w* confidence \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w all|strong="H7931"\w* \w the|strong="H7126"\w* ends \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H7126"\w* earth, \w And|strong="H1004"\w* \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w them|strong="H7126"\w* \w that|strong="H2691"\w* \w are|strong="H1004"\w* afar off \w upon|strong="H7931"\w* \w the|strong="H7126"\w* sea:

\w Who|strong="H3605"\w* \w by|strong="H3605"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* strength setteth fast \w the|strong="H3605"\w* mountains, Being girded \w about|strong="H3605"\w* \w with|strong="H3605"\w* might;

Who stilleth \w the|strong="H3559"\w* roaring \w of|strong="H2022"\w* \w the|strong="H3559"\w* seas, \w The|strong="H3559"\w* roaring \w of|strong="H2022"\w* \w their|strong="H3559"\w* waves, \w And|strong="H2022"\w* \w the|strong="H3559"\w* tumult \w of|strong="H2022"\w* \w the|strong="H3559"\w* peoples.

They also \w that|strong="H1995"\w* dwell \w in|strong="H3220"\w* \w the|strong="H7623"\w* uttermost parts \w are|strong="H1530"\w* afraid \w at|strong="H3220"\w* \w thy|strong="H7623"\w* tokens: Thou makest \w the|strong="H7623"\w* outgoings \w of|strong="H1995"\w* \w the|strong="H7623"\w* morning \w and|strong="H3220"\w* evening \w to|strong="H3220"\w* rejoice.

\w Thou|strong="H3427"\w* visitest \w the|strong="H3372"\w* earth, \w and|strong="H1242"\w* waterest \w it|strong="H1242"\w*, \w Thou|strong="H3427"\w* greatly enrichest \w it|strong="H1242"\w*; \w The|strong="H3372"\w* river \w of|strong="H3427"\w* God \w is|strong="H3427"\w* full \w of|strong="H3427"\w* water: \w Thou|strong="H3427"\w* providest \w them|strong="H3427"\w* grain, \w when|strong="H3427"\w* \w thou|strong="H3427"\w* hast \w so|strong="H3427"\w* prepared \w the|strong="H3372"\w* earth.

\w Thou|strong="H3588"\w* \w waterest|strong="H7783"\w* \w its|strong="H3588"\w* furrows \w abundantly|strong="H7227"\w*; \w Thou|strong="H3588"\w* settlest \w the|strong="H3588"\w* ridges \w thereof|strong="H4325"\w*: \w Thou|strong="H3588"\w* makest \w it|strong="H3588"\w* soft \w with|strong="H4390"\w* showers; \w Thou|strong="H3588"\w* blessest \w the|strong="H3588"\w* springing \w thereof|strong="H4325"\w*.
Thou crownest \w the|strong="H1288"\w* year \w with|strong="H7301"\w* \w thy|strong="H1288"\w* goodness; \w And|strong="H1288"\w* \w thy|strong="H1288"\w* paths drop fatness.

\w They|strong="H8141"\w* \w drop|strong="H7491"\w* \w upon|strong="H7491"\w* \w the|strong="H8141"\w* pastures \w of|strong="H8141"\w* \w the|strong="H8141"\w* wilderness; \w And|strong="H8141"\w* \w the|strong="H8141"\w* hills \w are|strong="H8141"\w* girded \w with|strong="H2896"\w* joy.

\w The|strong="H7491"\w* \w pastures|strong="H4999"\w* \w are|strong="H1524"\w* \w clothed|strong="H2296"\w* \w with|strong="H2296"\w* flocks; \w The|strong="H7491"\w* valleys also \w are|strong="H1524"\w* covered \w over|strong="H4999"\w* \w with|strong="H2296"\w* grain; They shout \w for|strong="H4057"\w* \w joy|strong="H1524"\w*, they also sing.
